title: Phan 21+ Discord
body:
Hello!

Last June, I circulated a post about setting up a discord for 21+ phans who wanted to have an adult, low stress, low pressure group chat to discuss phan, phanfic, and just general life. If you’re missing dan, if you’re wanting someone to talk to about phil’s videos, if you want to see some cat and dog photos – this is the place to come!

If you’re interested, there’s a brief FAQ from the link above, and there’s just a quick google form to fill out (its not to exclude, i’m just not super keen on giving out the link willy-nilly.)

If you have any questions, feel free to message me, if not… 

 Here’s the google forms link

and here is my disclaimer from the original post which still holds:

you don’t need to be following me, i don’t have a phandom blog, nor is it an attempt for me to get followers - i just want a place to chat to people about dnp because none of my friends are fans. [also if you are 16 & under please don’t follow me, i’m an adult.]
